--[[
    Autofarm loop:
    1) Go to sand and collect until pan is full
    2) Go to water and pan
    3) Shake until sand is gone
    4) On interval, pause farm, go Merchant, sell, then resume

    GUI:
    - Draggable/moveable window
    - Start/Stop toggle
    - AutoSell toggle
    - AutoLock / AutoUnlock ores toggle + separate lock/unlock ore dropdowns + custom add + save/load config
    - Record / Stop / Delete merchant way (with white dot visualization)
    - Fly toggle + speed slider
    - Type custom shake timing
    - Type merchant sell interval (minutes)
    - Set Sand/Water position buttons
    - Close button (stops farm + removes GUI)
]]

